PrecisAuthority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT with the Province of NEWFOUNDLAND which will amend the 1978 Agreement (as amended) so as to provide for the acquisition by the Government of Canada of three additional parcels of land containing an area of some 5.35 hectares which are to be annexed to TERRA NOVA NATIONAL PARK.
